{"tid":455616,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陰功豬喇【驚悚CCTV】祖孫3人碌落扶手梯 粗心媽推BB車婆婆跌穿頭","createTime":"2017-11-02T09:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T09:09:35.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7c3eb4576f3df654487ba02b86a76ed134a0e520","tid":455616,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T09:09:35.000Z","msg":"推嬰兒車還是搭電梯吧！江蘇南京地鐵一名張姓女子，近日推着嬰兒車搭扶手電梯，結果在扶手梯上沒站穩摔倒，嬰兒車內的女嬰也跟着翻側，走在前方的張女的母親見狀，趕來要扶起女兒和外孫女，結果也摔了下來。<br />\n事發於周日（10月29日）中午，張女的母親先上了電扶梯，張女推着女兒走在後方，疑嬰兒車沒有放好，張女想要調整卻失去平衡跌倒，結果自己、女兒和嬰兒車都摔下，張女母親要來救援也跟着摔倒，還當場頭破血流。由於3人倒在扶手梯上，其他乘客見狀急忙按下緊急掣，張女和女兒並沒有大礙。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171102&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57406823\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171102%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57406823&d=j2PRSKGdfq7iOjgrN1lG0fjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=5edaf250\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171102%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57406823&h=e7ca70f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171102&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57406823</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/02/170923_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F02%2F170923_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=b7f380c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銀芽銀芽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}